<p>
<lb n="1"/>tirumakaḷpolap peru<unclear>ṉi</unclear>lac celviyuṉ taṉakke Urimaippūṇṭamaiy maṉakkoḷa kāṉtaḷūrcālai kalamaṟuttaruḷi veṅkai ṉāṭuṅ kaṅ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ka pāṭi ṉuḷampapāṭiyuṉ taṭikaiy vaḻiyuṅ kuṭamalai nāṭuṅ kollamuṅ kaliṅkamum Eṇṭicai pukaḻ Īḻamaṇṭalamu Iraṭṭapāṭi Eḻarai Ilakkamu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>veṉṟa <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> k koṇṭu <unclear>tan</unclear>neḻil vaḷaruḻi Ūḻi Ellāyāṇṭuṉ toḻutakaiy viḷaṅkum yāṇṭey ceḻiyarait tecukoḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrīrājarājade</hi>vaṟkku yāṇṭu <num value="24">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 4</num> Ā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha">rājaśai <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> </hi>ṭāṇ <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> māṉ puḷḷiyā<unclear>ṇperiya</unclear> veḷmuttaraiyaṉukku perumāṉ tiruveṇṇāvallāṉ mullai<unclear>raipe</unclear>ru muttaraiyaṉ ṟaṇo
</p>

